Davido Music Worldwide (DMW) has released a new single, Mafa Mafa. The feel-good predicted hit is coming at a time when Nigerians and the world are gripped with the fears of the novel coronavirus. Mafa mafa, a certified street anthem has on it, Davido, The Flowolf, Peruzzi and Dremo. The song was produced by  Nakademus. Enjoy! In related news, Davido’s wife Chioma has tested positive for the coronavirus. According to the singer and CEO of DMW, his wife alongside 30 others decided to test for the virus after their return to Nigeria. Only his wife came out positive.